extendedInfo.description: Project Cloud is a social announcement platform for law students. It's a place where you can read announcements, ask questions and view the latest deadlines. The App will allow you to stay updated while on the move. To begin, go to HOME. Here, you can view all the latest announcements as well as those for the next two months. If you like an announcement, we have provided a SHARE buttonUnder CALENDAR, you will be able to view the announcements with their deadlines. If you find something that interests you here, simply click on HOME and read the announcement.The App also allows you to access our Facebook Page. You can now comment and like posts within the App. Finally, if you have any feedback or questions, click on Ask!

reviews.title: Great!
reviews.comment: Good app..auto updating notifications would make it undisputed..
